Frist of all
The following js files need to be added to your html file

1. jquery.counterup.min.js
2. waypoints.min.js

Now copy this jquery code and paste it into your jquery file
    
$(function() {

    $('.counter').counterUp({
                delay: 10,
                time: 1000
     });
     
});

Now,
The class name of the span tag will be > counter 

example : <span class="counter">1,234,567</span>
